{"tid":1513313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[9月1英領集會都要focus下啊!] 個petition 搞咁耐都未到10萬，去到集會你地其實想向英領表達咩?","createTime":"2019-08-28T09:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T12:25:09.000Z","uid":306816,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"d2d5fa6979d20c6b9546f3e73b44af817fb9923b","tid":1513313,"uid":306816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:27:08.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆， 英國已經有咁多份報章支持BNO平權。<br />\n<br />\n香港而架有成最少16/17萬個BNO holder ，但我地而架個petition 都未到10萬，咁究竟我地想人點幫我地?? <br />\n<br />\n未簽的就快d簽啦: <br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5PzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=23a9c6f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"fd355da61ab87512600746956ade2a4d2e37cab5","tid":1513313,"uid":306816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:32:09.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"14293cbe9ade5d8f5a6a8ee4d76724d29063a7dd","tid":1513313,"uid":306816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:32:19.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"37169232e988d61efc799f2be17a1d0aa6410de6","tid":1513313,"uid":306816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:33:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"880bfb836973d869e2f483cfbd17f2192b979cd1","tid":1513313,"uid":306816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:33:15.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e9ead4e27499466559715d481cc23363fb356bbf","tid":1513313,"uid":306816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:33:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b3852c963d76e536b88962d325c357114c4469df","tid":1513313,"uid":13489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vLJg16B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvLJg16B.gif&h=1befacd7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FqHEZTi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqHEZTi.gif&h=3d29e51e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（英國衛報）<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;中國單方面宣稱中英聯合聲明已經失效，身在香港嘅三百萬BN(O)持有人該何去何從？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>用1分鐘嘅時間簽名，務求收集到10萬簽名將BNO平權議題推上議會討論</strong></ins><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>為咗你自己，仲有你嘅摯愛，簽名？刻不容緩</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\nPostal Code 請填000000，如果身處英國就填所在地點嘅Code<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5PzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=23a9c6f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qpLVrd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qpLVrd.jpg&h=be822801&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XDnxAre.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXDnxAre.jpg&h=8e7cbffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">另外，9.1英領外和平集會，有意者請加入TG Channel或TG Group</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hzHddb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hzHddb.jpg&h=ed754444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9.1英領集會<br />\nTG Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/BritonsinHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FBritonsinHK&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5PzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=3738114c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/BritonsinHK</a><br />\nTG Group: