\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hzHddb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hzHddb.jpg&h=ed754444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9.1英領集會<br />\nTG Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/BritonsinHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FBritonsinHK&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5PzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=3738114c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/BritonsinHK</a><br />\nTG Group: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NLJJCVjMKArb7I1iP7CshQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNLJJCVjMKArb7I1iP7CshQ&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5PzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=2aad442e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NLJJCVjMKArb7I1iP7CshQ</a>"},{"pid":"c92efbf4b6e9342a5232fab4083922b6dca1c4d5","tid":1513313,"uid":116568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"828 Metoo集會<br />\n830 中環和平紀念碑默站<br />\n831 民陣遊行 <br />\n91 機場 <br />\n91 英領集會<br />\n92 三罷<br />\n93 三罷"},{"pid":"f9582200e4d5005013e09b29e9c7b1c387d40605","tid":1513313,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:15:38.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.28 停止國泰白色恐怖 愛丁堡廣場</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.28 #Metoo 遮打花園</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">8.31 民陣遊行 直指中聯辦</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.01 機場 13:00</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.02 全港三罷</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚見</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2