t is ignoring....&rdquo;呢個event. 原文大意係中國政府無視1981(其實應該係1984年)簽署嘅中英聯合聲明。如果We(英國政府)繼續對以上事件視而不見的話，將會造成災難。<br />\n<br />\n然後後邊嘅Hong Kongerd will come in as political refugees (其實佢漏咗個前因，for example 失去一國兩制後etc.)係解釋緊何為上邊提及嘅災難，同埋該災難將會為英國政府帶黎咩影響。<br />\n<br />\n條友係寫到1999，但你地keep住淨係focus係we will need....呢句而唔提前面果兩句，咁你地又有咩居心？"},{"pid":"0864ab40216bbce1420b31ba7f8d5304b1589afd","tid":1513313,"uid":304860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:20:00.000Z","msg":"we urge the parliament of British government to officially confirm the serious violation to Sino-British Joint declaration by the Chinese government!"},{"pid":"4077a0b923f547bebd4a809a466cccdb2284ca45","tid":1513313,"uid":143526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:20:15.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b745cd6680a697d2b2f6b6a200411d62a1152307","tid":1513313,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2d5fa6979d20c6b9546f3e73b44af817fb9923b","tid":1513313,"uid":306816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T09:27:08.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆， 英國已經有咁多份報章支持BNO平權。<br />\n<br />\n香港而架有成最少16/17萬個BNO holder ，但我地而架個petition 都未到10萬，咁究竟我地想人點幫我地?? <br />\n<br />\n未簽的就快d簽啦: <br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5PzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=23a9c6f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T11:20:33.000Z","msg":"快d簽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快d簽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快d簽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快d簽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快d簽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快d簽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27698c58b6