嘅Code<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5PzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=23a9c6f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2qpLVrd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2qpLVrd.jpg&h=be822801&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XDnxAre.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXDnxAre.jpg&h=8e7cbffc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">另外，9.1英領外和平集會，有意者請加入TG Channel或TG Group</span></span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hzHddb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hzHddb.jpg&h=ed754444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n9.1英領集會<br />\nTG Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/BritonsinHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FBritonsinHK&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5PzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=3738114c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/BritonsinHK</a><br />\nTG Group: <a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NLJJCVjMKArb7I1iP7CshQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNLJJCVjMKArb7I1iP7CshQ&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5PzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=2aad442e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NLJJCVjMKArb7I1iP7CshQ</a>"},{"pid":"3dd78a8399d596466bac4b124c437eea5378cd01","tid":1513313,"uid":306816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T17:05:08.000Z","msg":"咁多日 都仲有人留意 <br />\n再推一推"},{"pid":"4035bdddc7e9ce2b00027432cbbcc987190de054","tid":1513313,"uid":435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0